# 🦷 Apollonia Dental Practice — Management System

A full-stack MERN application for managing a dental practice, featuring role-based access control, patient management, appointments, meetings, and real-time notifications.

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Layer     | Technology                              |
|-----------|-----------------------------------------|
| Frontend  | React 18 · Vite · Tailwind CSS v3       |
| Backend   | Node.js · Express.js                    |
| Database  | MongoDB · Mongoose                      |
| Auth      | JWT (jsonwebtoken) · bcryptjs           |
| HTTP      | Axios                                   |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
apollonia-dental/
├── backend/
│   ├── app.js                  # Entry point
│   ├── .env                    # Environment variables
│   ├── config/
│   │   └── db.js               # MongoDB connection
│   ├── middleware/
│   │   └── auth.js             # JWT protect + adminOnly
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── User.js             # admin · doctor · staff · receptionist
│   │   ├── Employee.js         # Linked to User via userId
│   │   ├── Department.js       # name · description · color
│   │   ├── Patient.js          # Full patient profile
│   │   ├── Appointment.js      # patient · doctor · date · status
│   │   ├── Meeting.js          # title · participants · createdBy
│   │   ├── MedicalRecord.js    # diagnosis · treatment · prescription
│   │   └── Notification.js     # in-app notifications
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── auth.js             # login · register (admin) · user CRUD
│   │   ├── employees.js        # CRUD + available/users endpoint
│   │   ├── departments.js      # CRUD + employeeCount
│   │   ├── patients.js         # CRUD + medical records
│   │   ├── appointments.js     # CRUD + auto notifications
│   │   ├── meetings.js         # CRUD (admin creates)
│   │   ├── notifications.js    # read · mark as read
│   │   └── profile.js          # update own profile
│   └── seed/
│       └── seed.js             # Full test dataset
│
└── frontend/
    ├── index.html
    ├── vite.config.js          # Proxy /api → localhost:5000
    ├── tailwind.config.js
    └── src/
        ├── App.jsx             # Routes with role guards
        ├── index.css           # Global styles + Tailwind
        ├── api/
        │   └── axios.js        # Base URL + JWT interceptor
        ├── context/
        │   ├── AuthContext.jsx  # Auth state + localStorage
        │   └── NotifContext.jsx # Notifications polling (30s)
        ├── components/
        │   ├── Navbar.jsx           # Role router
        │   ├── AdminNavbar.jsx
        │   ├── DoctorNavbar.jsx     # With unread badge
        │   └── ReceptionistNavbar.jsx # With unread badge
        └── pages/
            ├── Login.jsx
            ├── Dashboard.jsx        # 3 personalized dashboards
            ├── Users.jsx            # Admin only
            ├── Employees.jsx        # Admin only
            ├── Departments.jsx      # Admin only
            ├── Patients.jsx         # Receptionist CRUD · Doctor read
            ├── Appointments.jsx     # Receptionist CRUD · Doctor read
            ├── Meetings.jsx         # Admin CRUD · Doctor read
            ├── Notifications.jsx    # Doctor + Receptionist
            └── Profile.jsx          # All roles
```

