## 🔌 API Endpoints

### Auth
```
POST   /api/auth/login           Public
POST   /api/auth/register        Admin only
GET    /api/auth/users           Admin only
PUT    /api/auth/users/:id       Admin only
DELETE /api/auth/users/:id       Admin only
GET    /api/auth/me              Authenticated
```

### Employees
```
GET    /api/employees                   Authenticated
GET    /api/employees/available/users   Authenticated
POST   /api/employees                   Authenticated
PUT    /api/employees/:id               Authenticated
DELETE /api/employees/:id               Authenticated
```

### Departments
```
GET    /api/departments        Authenticated
POST   /api/departments        Authenticated
PUT    /api/departments/:id    Authenticated
DELETE /api/departments/:id    Authenticated
```

### Patients
```
GET    /api/patients                        Authenticated
POST   /api/patients                        Admin · Receptionist
PUT    /api/patients/:id                    Admin · Receptionist
DELETE /api/patients/:id                    Admin · Receptionist
GET    /api/patients/:id/records            Authenticated
POST   /api/patients/:id/records            Admin · Doctor
PUT    /api/patients/:id/records/:rid       Admin · Doctor
DELETE /api/patients/:id/records/:rid       Admin · Doctor
```

### Appointments
```
GET    /api/appointments        Authenticated (doctor sees own)
POST   /api/appointments        Admin · Receptionist
PUT    /api/appointments/:id    Admin · Receptionist
DELETE /api/appointments/:id    Admin · Receptionist
```

### Meetings
```
GET    /api/meetings        Authenticated (doctor sees assigned)
POST   /api/meetings        Admin only
PUT    /api/meetings/:id    Admin only
DELETE /api/meetings/:id    Admin only
```

### Notifications
```
GET    /api/notifications              Authenticated
GET    /api/notifications/unread/count Authenticated
PUT    /api/notifications/:id/read     Authenticated
PUT    /api/notifications/read/all     Authenticated
```

### Profile
```
GET    /api/profile    Authenticated
PUT    /api/profile    Authenticated
```

---

## 🐳 Docker (optional)

```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

Services: `mongo` · `backend` (port 5000) · `frontend` (port 5173)

---

## 📝 Notes

- After running `seed.js`, clear localStorage in the browser before logging in
- JWT tokens expire after **7 days**
- Notifications are polled every **30 seconds** (no WebSocket required)
- The `receptionist` role cannot access Meetings or medical records
- Deleting a patient also deletes all associated medical records